CHANGELOG for Haskell Pdf Presenter
========================================

0.2.5
	* Fixed missing minus sign in negative times

0.2.4
	* Change keybinding for changing monitors from "S" to "M"
	* Fix positioning errors in the Glade GUI file
	* Terminology fix: "presenter window" not "screen" or "view"

0.2.3
	* Fix compilation on GHC 7.4

0.2.2
	* Fixes to cabal meta-data
	* Make sure all version numbers are up to date
	* Spell checking and proof reading

0.2.1
	* Added support for closing files
	* Added better time parsing
	* Added CHANGELOG

0.2
	* Initial release
